Package com.zebra.rfid.api3

Class Gen2v2

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zebra.rfid.api3.Gen2v2
  • public class Gen2v2
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles the Gen2v2 operations. Only Event based operations are supported Contains the parameter declaration and initialization of each Gen2v2 operation Contains the api's for the operations to be invoked by Application
